values: The biggest fear I have is that my girlfriend will leave me. Bottemline. I don't think she will, and I think deep down she knows that we'll be together forever. I mean we talk about it alot, about how we would raise kids and the type of house we'd live in. I know that God put us together for a reason. She will keep me on the right path, and I will make sure that she is safe and has somebody to turn to whenever. I can't help but feel like I'm still trying to prove myself. Fuck I don't know. I guess I'm just thinking way too much.

The first person to tell me happy birthday today is the only person to not call me on the other 19 birthdays...my dad. That was pretty interesting. Then I had Chinese food for dinner, and in my fortune cookie fortune, it stated that something unexpected would happen today...and sure enough when I was hanging with Ross, Noah came over, we had no idea he was home. I had more "happy birthdays" today then any other birthday I can remember. But the one person that I was waiting to here from the most, never called. I would trade all of them for the one call. I shouldn't care because I know that the one person is at Disneyland right now. But I still feel sad. I miss Amy.
Whats up everybody, it has been a long time since I posted anything on here. I think I might start to again though. Word...

...since I last posted here on live journal. I have been using myspace way more. Can't wai to see Bad Love Sessions again, it has been a long time. And We haven't all hung out in some time. I miss you guys.

This well be my last post for Live Journal, as I have no time between school and work, and other stuff that I do. It's not like I posted anyways. Maybe once school gets out I can post a little bit more, but as of right now, I am leaving.

Quoth the Tomato, Never More!

Today was really fun. I got out of bed just before breakfast because the smell of cooking bacon woke me up. I feel sad, because Sarah and Britney are complete bitches. They told everyone I have an STD, just because I slept with both of their boyfriends on Saturday night. I'm so hardcore. Me and Buzz went to the mall today, and I stole a whole heap of stuff. I got a Good Charlotte CD, a couple of DVDs and some new boots. Buzz got caught, but he fought his way out, and then we stole some lady's car and smashed it into a phone booth. Last night I had to shave my entire body. Apparently, the lice that I caught from Amanda's friend are really hard to get rid of. I look quite strange with no hair and eyebrows. I'd post pictures, but my webcam is broken. I want to tell the world to get fucked. I am sharpening my knives before I go to work today, because I'm going to cut out Robert's heart and feed it to him for losing my mail. Today, I got a digital camera! Yes! Here's some photos of my cock. I want to say thanks to simon and Abbey and Dave and the other Simon for helping me on Saturday. You guys are the best. By the way, if you happen to find my wallet, keys or underwear, could you SMS me? Adrian has my number. I went to the doctor yesterday, and he said I have bipolar disorder, which makes me different enough to be interesting, but the same as all the other cool people with bipolar disorder. You should all do this quiz! It's amazingly accurate. You just put in your name and birthday, and it will tell you what your favourite sexual position is. That's enough for now.
